      <title>法国在欧洲最安全债券市场中的地位面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/france-s-role-as-one-of-europe-s-safest-bond-markets-is-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于脆弱的少数派政府难以解决多年来一直存在的债务问题，法国作为欧洲最安全债券市场之一的地位有可能终结。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/france-s-role-as-one-of-europe-s-safest-bond-markets-is-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
